  • public class NormedRdCombinatorialToRdContinuous
extends NormedRdToNormedRd
    NormedRdCombinatorialToRdContinuous implements the f : Validated R^d Combinatorial To Validated R^d Continuous Normed Function Spaces. The Reference we've used is: - Carl, B., and I. Stephani (1990): Entropy, Compactness, and Approximation of Operators, Cambridge University Press, Cambridge UK.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
